    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This FD3S chassis features the legendary 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged rotary engine, delivering linear power through a crisp 5-speed manual transaxle. The vehicle maintains its factory-spec double-wishbone suspension geometry and aluminum control arms, providing exceptional unsprung weight management and tactile feedback. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive vacuum line overhaul and a cooling system refresh with an upgraded aluminum radiator to mitigate heat soak. The Torsen limited-slip differential remains tight, ensuring optimal torque distribution through the apex. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its age, the compression numbers are healthy across both rotors, and the primary-to-secondary boost transition remains seamless.",
      "price": 34500.0,
