    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sorted 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six. This unit delivers exceptional throttle response via its individual throttle bodies and a precision-calibrated double VANOS system. Power is managed through a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. Crucially, the rear subframe has been reinforced\u2014a vital preventative measure for this chassis\u2014and the rod bearings have been replaced to ensure long-term reciprocating assembly integrity. The suspension maintains its factory-spec kinematics with refreshed bushings, providing the communicative feedback expected of the E46 platform. While the aesthetics reflect a well-utilized driver\u2019s car, the drivetrain and structural vitals are robust and track-ready.",
